quran[12{c,v,t}:
20,65,"jadugar bolay"" moose, tum phenkhte ho ya pehlay hum phinkin? """
20,66,"moose ne kaha"" nahi, tum hi phenko"" yakayak unn ki rasiyaan aur unn ki lathyan unn ke jaadoo ke zor se moose ko daurti hui mehsoos honay lagen"
20,67,aur moose apne dil mein dar gaya
20,68,"hum ne kaha"" mat dar, to hi ghalib rahay ga"
20,69,"pheink jo kuch tairay haath mein hai, abhi inn ki saari banawati cheezon ko niglay jata hai yeh jo kuch bana kar laaye hain yeh to jadugar ka fraib hai, aur jadugar kabhi kamyaab nahi ho sakta, khuwa kisi shaan se woh aeye """
20,70,"aakhir ko yahi howa ke saaray jadugar sjday mein gira diye gay aur pukaar utthay"" maan liya hum ne haroon aur moose ke rab ko """
20,71,"firaon ne kaha"" tum imaan le aeye qabal is ke ke mein tumhe is ki ijazat deta? maloom ho gaya ke yeh tumhara guru hai jis ne tumhe jadoo gari sikhayi thi acha, ab mein tumahray haath paon mukhalif simtao se katwataا hon aur khajoor ke tnon par tum ko suli deta hon phir tumhe pata chal jaye ga ke hum dono mein se kis ka azaab ziyada sakht aur der pa hai"" ( yani mein tumhe ziyada sakht saza day sakta hon ya moose )"
20,72,"jadogaron ne jawab diya"" qasam hai uss zaat ki jis ne hamein peda kya hai, yeh hargiz nahi ho sakta ke hum roshan nishanain samnay aa jaane ke baad bhi ( sadaqat par ) tujhe tarjeeh den, too jo kuch karna chahay kar le to ziyada se ziyada bas isi duniya ki zindagi ka faisla kar sakta hai"
20,73,"hum to apne rab par imaan le aeye taakay woh hamari khataien maaf kar day aur is jadoo gari se, jis par to ne hamein majaboor kya tha, dar guzar farmaiye Allah hi acha hai aur wohi baqi rehne wala hai """
20,74,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo mujrim ban kar apne rab ke huzoor haazir hoga uss ke liye jahannum hai jis mein woh nah jie ga nah marey ga
20,75,"aur jo is ke huzoor momin ki hesiyat se haazir ho ga, jis ne naik amal kiye hon ge, aisay sab logon ke liye buland darjay hain"
20,76,"sada bahhar baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi, un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yeh jaza hai uss shakhs ki jo pakizgee ikhtiyar kere"
